statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from (select "terceros"."id", "terceros"."avatar", "terceros"."identificacion", "terceros"."nombres", "terceros"."apellidos", "terceros"."direccion", "ciudades"."nombre" as "ciudad", "terceros"."email", "roles"."name" as "rol", "tipos"."nombre" as "tipo" from "terceros" left join "ciudades" on "terceros"."ciudad_id" = "ciudades"."id" left join "roles" on "terceros"."rol_id" = "roles"."id" left join "tipos" on "tipos"."id" = "terceros"."tipo_id" where "terceros"."deleted_at" is null and "terceros"."deleted_at" is null order by "terceros"."id" asc) count_row_table

select count(*) as aggregate from (select "terceros"."id", "terceros"."avatar", "terceros"."identificacion", "terceros"."nombres", "terceros"."apellidos", "terceros"."direccion", "ciudades"."nombre" as "ciudad", "terceros"."email", "roles"."name" as "rol", "tipos"."nombre" as "tipo" from "terceros" left join "ciudades" on "terceros"."ciudad_id" = "ciudades"."id" left join "roles" on "terceros"."rol_id" = "roles"."id" left join "tipos" on "tipos"."id" = "terceros"."tipo_id" where "terceros"."deleted_at" is null and (LOWER(CAST("terceros"."identificacion" as TEXT)) LIKE '%log%' or LOWER(CAST("terceros"."nombres" as TEXT)) LIKE '%log%' or LOWER(CAST("terceros"."apellidos" as TEXT)) LIKE '%log%' or LOWER(CAST("terceros"."direccion" as TEXT)) LIKE '%log%') and "terceros"."deleted_at" is null order by "terceros"."id" asc) count_row_table

select "terceros"."id", "terceros"."avatar", "terceros"."identificacion", "terceros"."nombres", "terceros"."apellidos", "terceros"."direccion", "ciudades"."nombre" as "ciudad", "terceros"."email", "roles"."name" as "rol", "tipos"."nombre" as "tipo" from "terceros" left join "ciudades" on "terceros"."ciudad_id" = "ciudades"."id" left join "roles" on "terceros"."rol_id" = "roles"."id" left join "tipos" on "tipos"."id" = "terceros"."tipo_id" where "terceros"."deleted_at" is null and (LOWER(CAST("terceros"."identificacion" as TEXT)) LIKE '%log%' or LOWER(CAST("terceros"."nombres" as TEXT)) LIKE '%log%' or LOWER(CAST("terceros"."apellidos" as TEXT)) LIKE '%log%' or LOWER(CAST("terceros"."direccion" as TEXT)) LIKE '%log%') order by "terceros"."id" asc limit 10 offset 0
